<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA87">
<l>ippōtu miṉṉu miṉicciṟitu niṉṟālu</l>
<l>meppōtu mītēcol leṉṉeñcē yeppōtuṅ</l>
<l>kaikaḻalā nēmiyā ṉammēl viṉaikaṭivāṉ</l>
<l>meykaḻalē yētta muyal.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>All this time and again now, if you stand a little,</l>
<l>always speak only this, my heart. Always</l>
<l>strive to praise but the true anklet of him who chases away the Karma on me,</l>
<l>the one with the discus that does not get loose from [his] hand.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
